<font size="2"><b><i>1) DPD UK Mainland Delivery - Next working day delivery</i></b></font><br/>
<font size="2">Most of our items are sent out on a next working day delivery service. As long as the item offers this option, it will be with you on the next working day providing the following terms are met-</font></p><p><font size="2">
-The order is made before 1pm.</font></p><p><font size="2">
