 <br/>
<b><u>PLEASE NOTE</u></b></font></p><p><font size="2">
-The service provided is a next WORKING day service. As a result, items will not be delivered on Bank Holidays. Furthermore, Bank Holidays will delay the delivery of orders if they are made after the cut-off point.</font></p><p><font size="2">
-A Saturday delivery is available on skatehut.co.uk if you require this.</font></p><p><font size="2">
- s made on a Friday before 1pm will be received on the following Monday. </font></p><p><font size="2">
- s placed after 1pm on Friday will be dispatched on Monday for delivery on Tuesday.</font></p><p><font size="2">
 <br/>


<font size="2"><i><b>2) Royal Mail - 2-6 working day delivery.</b></i><br/></font>
<font size="2">In addition to this service, a lot of our lower priced items are sent via Royal Mail. This is often free and usually takes 2-6 working days to reach our customers.</font></font></p><p><font size="2"><font size="2">
Please note, this service will be delayed during Bank Holiday periods.</font></font></p><p><font size="2"><font size="2"><br/>

<font size="2"><i><b>3) Hermes Tracked - 3-5 working day delivery.</b></i><br/></font>
<font size="2">This is available for £2.65 and usually takes less time that the 3-5 days stated. This is an ideal option if you want a cheap alternative to DPD delivery.</font></font></font></p><p><font size="2"><font size="2"><font size="2">
Please note, this service will be delayed during Bank Holiday periods.</font></font></font></p><p><font size="2"><font size="2"><font size="2"><br/>

<i><b>4) DPD European Delivery - 2-7 working day delivery</b></i><br/>
Where available, some of our items are eligible for delivery to Europe. This usually takes 2-7 working days.</font></font></font></p><p><font size="2"><font size="2"><font size="2">
Please ensure to include a contact e-mail address and phone number which we can pass on to the courier. Failure to do so may result in a delayed or failed delivery.</font></font></font></p><p><font size="2"><font size="2"><font size="2"> 
